\v 16 Mamar…ô, dongki kafan r…®mnhek in tuk norien has kafan. K…®taw…ô kharkun m…ô dongki to rap…ôh n…ôgkiarien, m…ôr…®g Kughen r…®mnor m…ô dongki tukr…ôgkiar r…ômhen k…®n yermam…ô ram…ôgkiar m…ô tukr…®ni-…ôhu norien …ôt…ôwao kape profet a.\f + \fr 2:16 \ft  Tak…ôm stori kape Balam m…®ne dongki ye Nam 22:28-35.\f*   
\p
