\v 20 M…ôr…®g tukm…ô iri…ô k…®sap ta ye nahasien kape tokrei tan…ô n…®p…®g kw…ônhau…ô mharkun Yesu Yermaru yame Rav…ôh M…®ragh …ôtaw…ô, m…ôkneik…®n, m…®sarar, mamharer…®g-p…ôn tuk norien kape t…ôvhag…ô has, m…ôkneik…®n norien has ramarmaru ir…ôri…ô. Iri…ô kas…ôm…®r ye nahasien yame rahas rapita yame k…®m…®sar…ô iran kup…ôn.  
